messages.message:
btw this issue only occurred for my PR, and other PRs did not have this issue

in case you see similar issues for your PR, i resolved this by deleting the sandbox from the crafting side (search for the sandbox in https://instabase.sandboxes.site/sandboxes) and re-running Cypress CI

for some reason, the crafting sandbox was stuck in “Launching” state, so deleting and re-creating solved the issue
